{"tid":322873,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[JUPAS 最後排位] 八大起薪點：港大領先，教大第二，嶺大有進步空間","createTime":"2017-07-15T07:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T14:26:41.000Z","uid":123308,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19ea040c1d3eb65e8303ea2f34266c16be56e310","tid":322873,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:31:46.000Z","msg":"17:35 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2016</span>/07/22<br />\n八大畢業生薪酬升6% 副學士僅34%全職就業<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1468986/八大畢業生薪酬升6-%20副學士僅34-全職就業\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1468986%2F%E5%85%AB%E5%A4%A7%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%9F%E8%96%AA%E9%85%AC%E5%8D%876-%2520%E5%89%AF%E5%AD%B8%E5%A3%AB%E5%83%8534-%E5%85%A8%E8%81%B7%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD&d=eue%2FMUzPyBi8wleLr1e%2Fc7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=124b4457\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1468986/八大畢業生薪酬升6-%20副學士僅34-全職就業</a><br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;八所大學院校之中，<ins>畢業生平均年薪最高為<strong>香港大學</strong></ins>，平均年薪有26.3萬元，即月薪平均有2.1萬元；<ins>畢業生年薪僅次於港大的是剛正名的<strong>香港教育大學</strong></ins>，畢業生年薪平均亦有26萬元，平均月薪為2.1萬元，估計與畢業生較多從事教席有關，因現行學位教師起薪點約為2.2萬元；<ins>最低為<strong>嶺南大學</strong>畢業生</ins>，平均年薪僅16.1萬元，即月薪約1.3萬多元。&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n18:20 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2016</span>/07/22<br />\n教大 KO 中大 一幅圖睇晒8大起薪有幾高<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1469011/教大%20KO%20中大%20%20%20%20一幅圖睇晒8大起薪有幾高\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1469011%2F%E6%95%99%E5%A4%A7%2520KO%2520%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%2520%2520%2520%2520%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%85%E5%9C%96%E7%9D%87%E6%99%928%E5%A4%A7%E8%B5%B7%E8%96%AA%E6%9C%89%E5%B9%BE%E9%AB%98&d=eue%2FMUzPyBi8wleLr1e%2Fc7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=5d8f996b\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1469011/教大%20KO%20中大%20%20%20%20一幅圖睇晒8大起薪有幾高</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1465000/1469011/graduate_salary_thumb_20160722_v3_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1465000%2F1469011%2Fgraduate_salary_thumb_20160722_v3_1024.jpg&h=34e9572f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;當中首3位是<ins><strong>港大</strong></ins>、<ins><strong>教大</strong></ins>及<ins><strong>中大</strong></ins>，<ins>最高的<strong>港大</strong>畢業生</ins>，平均年薪26.3萬元，每月約21,916元；而<ins><strong>教大</strong>自11/12年後再次超越<strong>中大</strong></ins>，年薪26萬元，每月約21,666元。&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>教大</ins></strong>平均年薪高於<strong><ins>中大</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n教資會的調查數據由教資會資助院校每年在12月期間進行的畢業生就業統計調查所搜集，由於現時<ins>8大資助課程</ins>中，只有<ins><strong>港大</strong></ins>及<ins><strong>中大</strong></ins>設有<ins>醫科</ins>，亦令這兩間大學畢業生平均年薪較高。<br />\n<br />\n但根據調查結果，今次以<ins>教育科目為主的<strong>教大</strong></ins>，畢業生年薪<ins>超過<strong>中大</strong>排行第2</ins>，而<strong><ins>教大</ins></strong><ins>的畢業生平均年薪於11/12年亦為8大之首</ins>，相信跟教大畢業生多數從事教師等職業有關。<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n18:22 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2016</span>/07/04<br />\n港大 VS 中大 一幅圖睇晒8大院校起薪點<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1457457/一幅圖睇晒大學「神科」人工有幾高？\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1457457%2F%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%85%E5%9C%96%E7%9D%87%E6%99%92%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E3%80%8C%E7%A5%9E%E7%A7%91%E3%80%8D%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%89%E5%B9%BE%E9%AB%98%EF%BC%9F&d=eue%2FMUzPyBi8wleLr1e%2Fc7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=b8bb288f\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1457457/一幅圖睇晒大學「神科」人工有幾高？</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1455000/1456814/graduatetable4_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1455000%2F1456814%2Fgraduatetable4_1024.jpg&h=8f17e181&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫科教育年薪最高<br />\n<br />\n大學的平均年薪高低亦跟其學科有關，過去7年<ins>醫科</ins>、<ins>牙科</ins>及<ins>護理科</ins>畢業生的<ins>平均年薪最高</ins>，13/14年的年薪為37.9萬元（每月約3.2萬元），其次為<ins>教育科</ins>（每月約2.1萬元）及<ins>工程</ins>和<ins>科技科</ins>（每月約1.7萬元）。<br />\n<br />\n而<ins>文科</ins>和<ins>人文科學科</ins>的年薪最低，年薪16.5萬元，每月約1.4萬元。<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n16:07 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2016</span>/07/05<br />\n一幅圖睇晒大學「神科」人工有幾高？<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1457457/一幅圖睇晒大學「神科」人工有幾高？\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1457457%2F%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%85%E5%9C%96%E7%9D%87%E6%99%92%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E3%80%8C%E7%A5%9E%E7%A7%91%E3%80%8D%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%89%E5%B9%BE%E9%AB%98%EF%BC%9F&d=eue%2FMUzPyBi8wleLr1e%2Fc7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=b8bb288f\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1457457/一幅圖睇晒大學「神科」人工有幾高？</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1455000/1457457/u_grade_thumb_20160705_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1455000%2F1457457%2Fu_grade_thumb_20160705_1024.jpg&h=0a07f419&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近年工程和科技學科年薪上升<br />\n<br />\n過去10年的數據顯示，<ins>醫科</ins>、<ins>牙科</ins>和<ins>護理科</ins>的平均年薪一直最高，而<ins>教育科僅次</ins>，兩者於06/07年起的平均年薪分別維持在30萬元以上及20萬元以上。<br />\n<br />\n不過13/14年，<ins>工程科</ins>和<ins>科技科</ins>的平均年薪為20.7萬元，首次超越20萬元。其實自11/12年起，工程學科的平均年薪便超越商科和管理科，<ins>成為平均年薪排第3主要學科</ins>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年好似未出？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"643a0be5eaa93264dc534b0e313727b8f3a81019","tid":322873,"uid":22309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:12:27.000Z","msg":"In engine, we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a590d8195e3a7ec280f956e2202f76b83affa2c","tid":322873,"uid":17530,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T10:49:38.000Z","msg":"東大起薪<br />\nMls of rd : 27000~<br />\nNursing : 30000~<br />\n總論：東大世界第一"},{"pid":"ede5292de21d4a2bd322ced49defd099ef24cc7f","tid":322873,"uid":34876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T10:52:16.000Z","msg":"工程及科技科 包埋it?"},{"pid":"6074dac043cd384b8f85f5d1873ce85842f43b18","tid":322873,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T12:49:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東大起薪<br />\nMls of rd : 27000~<br />\nNursing : 30000~<br />\n總論：東大世界第一</blockquote><br />\n有冇非八大資料數據？都真係值得參考<br />\n<br />\n不過東大可能要幾年後有畢業生先有數據"},{"pid":"bc82cfc4fa0f06bd70ad0b50ca2ee3aaa11225a6","tid":322873,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>工程及科技科 包埋it?</blockquote><br />\n電子工程我諗算掛 (?)"},{"pid":"05884e63cb08391069aa55f501a960abee0e6032","tid":322873,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:51:18.000Z","msg":"有咩科排jupas排bandE都仲會入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01915adffd270f5daa5ecf18018c9c7478450f7f","tid":322873,"uid":91244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T16:24:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>東大起薪<br />\nMls of rd : 27000~<br />\nNursing : 30000~<br />\n總論：東大世界第一</blockquote><br />\n有冇非八大資料數據？都真係值得參考<br />\n<br />\n不過東大可能要幾年後有畢業生先有數據</blockquote><br />\n非八大應該得I大同東大有得揮"},{"pid":"8b86c29abf22c9c12706cb6e76afeb31b83455e9","tid":322873,"uid":128857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T16:47:15.000Z","msg":"其實讀過下stat既都知入息一定係計中位數唔係平均數, 否則一定會比部分人(例如醫療科)拉高哂, 有D大學明顯唔準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea363369d0024b6d9ae629478135a25c2f3860b","tid":322873,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:43:14.000Z","msg":"見有 post 講性價比，我諗呢個